5 Fifty Dollars ($50.00) or the cost of the search, whichever is the
6 lesser amount. The fees shall be deposited in the OSBI Revolving
7 Fund. The Oklahoma State Bureau of Investigation shall provide the
8 national criminal history record check to the Secretary of State
